<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Weather Forecast News</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #121212;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #1f1f1f;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        main {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .news-section {
            flex: 1;
            background-color: #1f1f1f;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .news-section img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .news-section h2 {
            margin: 10px 0 5px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        .news-section p {
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

    </style>
    <script>
        function openDetail(url) {
            window.open(url, '_blank');
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Weather Forecast News</h1>
    </header>
    
    <main>
        <section class="news-section" onclick="openDetail('https://www.indiatoday.in/weather/delhi-weather-forecast-today')">
            <img src="delhi-winter-image.jpg" alt="Weather Update">
            <h2>Cold wave getting better of the Capital</h2>
            <p>Delhi Temperatures Drop 4 Degrees Below Normal on Monday Morning as Cold Wave Grips City!</p>
        </section>

        <section class="news-section" onclick="openDetail('https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/mumbai/mumbai-boat-accident-indian-navy-chief-to-visit-today-for-investigation-search-operations-under-way/articleshow/116491598.cms')">
            <img src="storm image.jpg" alt="Rain Forecast">
            <h2>Tough times in ocean for Indian Navy</h2>
            <p>Navy Speedboat Loses Control and Collides With Mumbai Ferry, Killing At Least 13 Individuals.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="news-section" onclick="openDetail('https://weather.com/en-IN/india/news/news/2024-12-21-40-day-chillai-kalan-begins-in-kashmir-coldwave-and-snowfall-likely')">
            <img src="winter image.jpg" alt="Winter Weather">
            <h2>Winter lands in Northern India</h2>
            <p>Kashmir Plunges into 40-Day Chillai Kalan; Intense Coldwave, Snowfall Expected Through Christmas.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    
</body>
</html>